    • Method Detail

      • deserialize

        ServiceResponse deserialize(SOAPMessage message)
        Deserializes the given SOAPMessage object to ServiceResponse object.
        Parameters:
        message - SOAP message to be deserialized
        Returns:
        ServiceResponse object that represents the given SOAPMessage object; if the operation fails, null is returned

      • deserialize

        ServiceResponse deserialize(SOAPMessage message,
                          String producerNamespaceURI)
        Deserializes the given SOAPMessage object to ServiceResponse object. If service producer's namespace URI is given, then it's used for finding the response from the SOAP mesagge's body. Value "*" means that the namespace is ignored.
        Parameters:
        message - SOAP message to be deserialized
        producerNamespaceURI - service producer's namespace URI
        Returns:
        ServiceResponse object that represents the given SOAPMessage object; if the operation fails, null is returned
